			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: MUST READ: 8th Shawl with 4 Peeps (Bard Power)<a name="34281"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 12 04 6:42 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>You can also highsun the dwarf guy each time the waves spawn.  Keep someone at his spawn point to aggro him and keep him busy while you kite the giants/wolves etc away.  You can Fade them out of the way of everything, or camp if you don't have fade - they will stay there permanently until you are ready to kill them.  Do this until he paths all the way to get your shawl - bingo - shawl with no killing at all.  Do this with one other person, then grab a few more for the killings to make it go fast.  Position the people at each camp, and kite the previously placed mobs around.  Highsun a single to them when they are ready, and then repeat until all are dead.  Remember which group of mobs goes to which camp when doing this, otherwise you'll have no problems.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
